title: Where Do You Kindred?
body: I'm doing a poll to see where people like to play Kindred. I have a few responses so far but I need A LOT more to get any that are statistically significant. I posted my findings so far [on Reddit](https://www.reddit.com/r/leagueoflegends/comments/3otquc/where_do_you_like_to_see_kindred_short_poll/). Thanks for your responses in advance!
